title: Passport officers using face recognition technology better at detecting fraud (UNSW - The University of ...
text: ( Source : UNSW - The University of New South Wales ) Face-matching experts using automatic face recognition software at the Australian Passport Office are 20% more accurate than average people at detecting fraud, new research shows.
